es for Asynchronous Sleepable Tasks","href":"/tutorials/features/bpf_wq/","depth":2},{"title":"eBPF Tutorial by Example: BPF Dynamic Pointers for Variable-Length Data","href":"/tutorials/features/dynptr/","depth":2},{"title":"eBPF Tutorial: Extending Kernel Subsystems with BPF structops","href":"/tutorials/features/struct_ops/","depth":2},{"title":"eBPF by Example: Building a GPU Flamegraph Profiler with CUPTI","href":"/tutorials/xpu/flamegraph/","depth":2},{"title":"eBPF Tutorial by Example: Monitoring GPU Driver Activity with Kernel Tracepoints","href":"/tutorials/xpu/gpu-kernel-driver/","depth":2},{"title":"eBPF Tutorial by Example: Tracing Intel NPU Kernel Driver Operations","href":"/tutorials/xpu/npu-kernel-driver/","depth":2}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}